features: WORKS WITH LINUS L2: The Yale Dot serves as an ideal complement to your Yale Linus Smart Lock L2 and Yale Conexis L2 to add even more convenience to your home access routine.
TAP TO (UN)LOCK: Simply tap your phone onto the Yale Dot to effortlessly unlock or lock your front door without opening the app.
WI-FI (UN)LOCKING: (Un)lock your door anywhere with a tap. Place a Yale Dot in your home office for easy access while working or by your bedside for nighttime security.

BLUETOOTH (UN)LOCKING: Guests can tap to (un)lock when nearby. Place the Yale Dot outside your front door to allow unlocking for your trusted visitors. Access rights are managed and updated through the Guest List in the Yale Home app.

PACK OF 3: Position your three Yale Dots according to your preference around your home or anywhere (when using Wi-Fi) and relish keyless convenience tailored to your needs. Linus L2 supports pairing up to 5 Yale Dots.
description: From the manufacturer Say goodbye to the annoying search for keys at your front door or losing keys The Yale Linus Smart Lock L2 is designed with safety and comfort in mind. It automatically locks as soon as you close and unlock your door when you are nearby. It can also be programmed to unlock and lock at certain times of the day. Use the Yale Home app to give trusted people access with your smartphone and see when your door has been opened thanks to the detailed activity feed. Increase comfort with other keyless accessories such as the Yale Dot or the Yale Smart Keypad. Features: 3 Pack Yale Dots NFC access Compatible with Yale Linus Smart Lock L2 Works with the Yale Home app Linus L2 supports up to 5 Yale Dots Share access with trusted people Supports Wi-Fi remote control for owners Supports Bluetooth for guests Simply stop to (un)lock Simply hold your smartphone on to the Yale Dot to open or lock without opening the app, providing more convenience for your access to your home. Place it anywhere Owners can open and close from anywhere by stopping on the Yale Dot. Place the Yale Dot in your office so you can easily access it while working, or next to your bed so you are safe at night. Bluetooth unlocking Place the Yale Dot outside your home near your front door to allow trusted visitors to lock open and make keyless access to your home easier. Multiple dots Place up to 5 dots in different places in your house to control your smart lock from a distance with a single hand movement, allowing keyless comfort according to your wishes.
